uncles and aunties to their wedding.

10:34.320 --> 10:35.160
Nice!

10:35.280 --> 10:36.760
You first take that stance, right?

10:37.160 --> 10:38.280
-Oh, like this.
-Anchors have this--

10:38.360 --> 10:39.200
Yeah.

10:39.280 --> 10:42.520
Local couple calls
themselves COVID positive

10:43.080 --> 10:48.000
to avoid inviting uncles
and aunties to their wedding!

10:50.440 --> 10:52.280
-Have to stare, it's very…
