10:52.360 --> 10:53.200
Very important!

10:53.280 --> 10:55.760
Audiences should take in
how much injustice is happening

10:55.880 --> 10:57.400
-to uncle and aunt, right?
-Right.

10:57.480 --> 10:58.640
So, that is the second part.

10:58.880 --> 11:00.680
And the third part
is obviously the camera,

11:00.760 --> 11:02.200
which I will go to the camera and do.

11:02.280 --> 11:04.160
-But come. You can try.
-Come on, Atul. Go for it.

11:07.360 --> 11:08.240
The pens…

11:08.520 --> 11:09.440
So, you have to be bigger, man!

11:09.520 --> 11:11.480
So, like, push your hand down
on the table.

11:11.560 --> 11:13.080
-Yeah, like this?
-Yeah. Lean forward.

11:13.160 --> 11:14.480
-Lean forward.
-Be angry.

11:14.840 --> 11:17.760
So, as an audience, I feel like
I'm standing in front of this man

11:17.960 --> 11:20.560
who's leaning in on me cause
what he's saying is so important!

11:21.080 --> 11:24.880
This year, the film awards
will be held at the NCB office,

11:25.360 --> 11:26.720
since they're anyway present there.

11:29.480 --> 11:31.080
Atul, what was that?

11:32.320 --> 11:33.760
-Do you wanna try? You wanna try?
-Yes, of course.

11:35.280 --> 11:36.840
So, okay. Sapan, give me a stance.

11:36.920 --> 11:39.120
Now, I wanna show you
a new camera trick, right?

11:39.200 --> 11:40.520
-Okay.
-So, we call this the cobra,

11:40.600 --> 11:42.600
where the camera is doing its own thing.

11:42.920 --> 11:44.880
So, you have to just
constantly follow the lens.

11:44.960 --> 11:46.800
-Oh, I have to follow that also.
-He will come in,

11:46.920 --> 11:48.680
he will go out,
he will move around.

11:48.880 --> 11:54.320
The idea is, this pointless,
needless movement adds stress.

11:54.480 --> 11:56.720
-Yeah.
-Three, two, one, cue.

11:56.920 --> 11:58.440
Breaking news!

