Local vegetable vendor Rakesh
becomes the richest man in India

12:02.880 --> 12:05.080
after hoarding two dozen avocados.

12:07.440 --> 12:10.200
-I love the fireworks and the…
-There was a flare!

12:10.320 --> 12:11.560
-Wow!
-It was amazing!

